name: SportRack J-Stacker Kayak Carrier
description: This roof-top kayak carrier needs no adjustment, just lift your boat, place it on, and secure it with the tie downs.Fits  most manufacturer's or aftermarket crossbars (max. 9cm crossbar diameter).Includes 2 heavy-duty, tie-down straps with cam-buckle and 2 ropes with galvanized steel bumper hooks.Attachment hardware is quick to install and remove.
